---
layout: layout.njk
title: Salary Guides for Tech Roles
metaTitle: "Tech Salary Guides | Askia Blog"
metaDescription: "Structured tech salary guides for DevOps, SRE, platform, and cloud roles built to help candidates understand bands, leverage, and negotiation angles."
breadcrumbs:
  - name: "Home"
    url: "/"
  - name: "Resources"
    url: "/resources/"
  - name: "Career Intelligence"
    url: "/blog/"
  - name: "Salary Guides"
    url: "/blog/salary/"
---
<section class="blog-hero">
  <div class="container blog-hero-grid">
    <div class="blog-hero-copy">
      <p class="hero-eyebrow">Compensation Mastery</p>
      <h1 class="blog-hero-title">Salary Guides Inside the Blog</h1>
      <p class="blog-hero-subtitle">Structured pay guides for technical roles, designed as a searchable blog sublibrary instead of another flat pile of posts.</p>
      <div class="blog-hero-actions">
        <a class="btn btn-primary" href="/salary-negotiation/">Get Salary Negotiation Help</a>
        <a class="btn btn-ghost" href="/blog/interview/">Browse Interview Guides</a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="blog-hero-media">
      <div class="blog-hero-image">
        <img src="/assets/blog/offer-range.jpg" alt="Career compensation planning visuals." loading="eager" fetchpriority="high" />
        <span class="holo-badge">PAY SIGNAL</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section blog-grid-section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="blog-grid">
      {% for post in collections.publicSalaryBlog | reverse %}
      <article class="blog-card">
        <a class="blog-card-image" href="{{ post.url }}">
          <img src="{{ post.data.featuredImage }}" alt="{{ post.data.imageAlt }}" loading="lazy" />
        </a>
        <div class="blog-card-body">
          <div class="blog-card-meta">
            {% for category in post.data.categories %}
              <span class="category-pill">{{ category }}</span>
            {% endfor %}
          </div>
          <h2><a href="{{ post.url }}">{{ post.data.title }}</a></h2>
          <p>{{ post.data.description }}</p>
          <div class="blog-card-foot">
            <span>{{ post.data.readTime }}</span>
            <span>{{ post.data.publishDate }}</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </article>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
